title: Audio Cambridge Advanced Dictionary  4.3.128 Full[X8]
description:
The best Audio Cambridge Advance English learner's dictionary is better than ever, with new words, audio pronunciations and new features. 
Based on the world's largest corpus of American English, the Cambridge Dictionary of American English provides up-to-date vocabulary, easy-to-understand definitions, helpful usage notes, and examples that show how English is really used. The second edition offers advanced search features and a thesaurus. The audio version features spoken pronunciations for every word.
